            <h2 class="section-title">About the Championship</h2>
            <p>Every year in mid-January, hundreds of elite university dance teams travel to the Walt Disney World Resort in Orlando, Florida. They compete head-to-head for the legendary white jackets and National Title trophies. This platform celebrates the intersection of elite athleticism, artistry, and university spirit.</p>
            
